1289.name: L-Ag18P
1289.Applications:
Particularly recommended for sanitary and refrigerating installations, boilers, heat exchangers, tubing etc. Do not use in a sulphurous environment.
For working temperatures up to 200ºC
1289.Suitable_For: Copper to copper (without flux). Brass, copper and copper-tin alloys (with flux). Do not use in a sulphurous environment.
